  <front>
   <head>The EQUIPAGE. Written Originally in FRENCH by L'Abbé Reigner.</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1" stanza_type="couplet">
     <l n="1" met="+-|+-|+-|+-" line_length="8">SInce the Road of Life's so ill;</l>
     <l n="2" met="+-|+-|+-|+-" line_length="8">I, to pass it, use this Skill,</l>
     <l n="3" met="+-|+-|+-|+-" line_length="8">My frail  driving home</l>
     <l n="4" met="+-|+-|+-|+-" line_length="8">To its latest Stage, the</l>
     <l n="5" met="+-|+-|+-|+-" line_length="8">first, in Harness strong,</l>
     <l n="6" met="+-|+-|+-|+-" line_length="8">Marches stedfastly along:</l>
     <l n="7" met="+-|+-|+-|+-" line_length="8">to smooth the Pace,</l>
     <l n="8" met="+-|+-|+-|+-" line_length="8">Fills the next adjoining Trace:</l>
     <l n="9" met="+-|+-|+-|+-" line_length="8">leads the Way,</l>
     <l n="10" met="+-|+-|+-|+-" line_length="8">Whom no heavy Curb do's sway;</l>
     <l n="11" met="+-|+-|+-|+-" line_length="8">an equal Part sustains,</l>
     <l n="12" met="+-|+-|+-|+-" line_length="8">All indulg'd the loosen'd Reins:</l>
     <l n="13" met="+-|+-|+-|+-" line_length="8">In the Box sits vig'rous</l>
     <l n="14" met="+-|+-|+-|+-" line_length="8">Shunning miry Paths of Wealth:</l>
     <l n="15" met="+-|+-|+-|+-" line_length="8">with easy Smiles,</l>
     <l n="16" met="+-|+-|+-|+-" line_length="8">Ev'ry harsher Step beguiles;</l>
     <l n="17" met="+-|+-|+-|+-" line_length="8">Whilst of Nature, or of Fate</l>
     <l n="18" met="+-|+-|+-|+-" line_length="8">Only This I wou'd intreat:</l>
     <l n="19" met="+-|+-|+-|+-" line_length="8">The  might not decay,</l>
     <l n="20" met="+-|+-|+-|+-" line_length="8">Till the worn  drops away.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
